":24,"verse":21,"text":"For Raabia, the chief ,","searchKeywords":["for","raabia","the","chief"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_22","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":22,"text":"and for Isaari, Salomoth: for the sons of Salomoth, Jath.","searchKeywords":["and","for","isaari","salomoth","the","sons","jath"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_23","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":23,"text":"The sons of Ecdiu; Amadia the second, Jaziel the third, Jecmoam the fourth.","searchKeywords":["the","sons","ecdiu","amadia","second","jaziel","third","jecmoam","fourth"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_24","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":24,"text":"For the sons of Oziel, Micha: the sons of Micha; Samer.","searchKeywords":["for","the","sons","oziel","micha","samer"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_25","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":25,"text":"The brother of Micha; Isia, the son of Isia; Zacharia.","searchKeywords":["the","brother","micha","isia","son","zacharia"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_26","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":26,"text":"The sons of Merari, Mooli, and Musi: the sons of Ozia,","searchKeywords":["the","sons","merari","mooli","and","musi","ozia"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_27","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":27,"text":"of Merari by Ozia,—his sons Isoam, and Sacchur, and Abai.","searchKeywords":["merari","ozia","his","sons","isoam","and","sacchur","abai"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_28","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":28,"text":"To Mooli Eleazar, and Ithamar; and Eleazar died, and had no sons.","searchKeywords":["mooli","eleazar","and","ithamar","died","had","sons"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_29","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":29,"text":"For Kis; the sons of Kis; Jerameel.","searchKeywords":["for","kis","the","sons","jerameel"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_30","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":30,"text":"And the sons of Musi; Mooli, and Eder, and Jerimoth. These the sons of the Levites according to the houses of their families.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","musi","mooli","eder","jerimoth","these","levites","according","houses","their","families"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_24_31","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":24,"verse":31,"text":"And they also received lots as their brethren the sons of Aaron before the king; Sadoc also, and Achimelech, and the chiefs of the families of the priests and of the Levites, principal heads of families, even as their younger brethren.","searchKeywords":["and","they","also","received","lots","their","brethren","the","sons","aaron","before","king","sadoc","achimelech","chiefs","families","priests","levites","principal","heads","even","younger"]}]